安装 Vundle

git clone https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim

配置vimrc
" ----------------------------- Vundle Start -----------------------------
set nocompatible
filetype off
set rtp+=~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim
call vundle#begin()
Plugin 'VundleVim/Vundle.vim'

call vundle#end()
filetype plugin indent on
" ----------------------------- Vundle End   -----------------------------"

:PluginInstall 安装配置好的插件
:PluginClean 清理不在配置范围内的插件
:PluginUpdate 更新插件
:PluginSearch  查找插件
